{"about_the_game":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle for dominion over the lands alone or with friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose one of several playable races and recruit powerful heroes to lead your armies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a rich 3D game world, where each faction spreads its unique biome.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect powerful items and cast spells with devastating effects to wipe out enemy armies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deep RPG progression systems allow each character to specialize in a myriad of ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Random map generator and quest systems ensure no two game sessions feel the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lovingly hand-crafted by a small team - No AI generated models, textures or code.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007650/extras/Paladinshowcase_gifloop.gif?t=1728374446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our Development Roadmap</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Q1-Q4 2023 - Design, Business Set-up, Team Building, Prototyping</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Q1 2024 - Map Generation, Basic Objects, Basic Actions, Basic UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Q2 2024 - Battlefield Combat, Map Skills, VFX, Victory and Defeat, Saving and Loading</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Q3 2024 - Resource Buildings, Provinces, NPCs, Items, Quests, Steam Page</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Q4 2024 - Gameplay Trailer, Kingdom Tech, Talent Trees, Improved Fog of War and Controls, More POIs, Day/Night Cycles, Diplomacy, Outside Game Loop, Demo Release</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Q1-Q4 2025 - Final Release, More Races, More Game Modes, Online Multiplayer and More..</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3007650?t=1728374446","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steams